  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Detective Report:

    The Golden Speaking Ball disappeared from the Academy.
    Mrs Frogman sent the detective to investigate the classroom. The Lunch Lady said
    that Mr Whinnyham did not collect his apples and carrots. Mr Whinnyham''s shop
    was already open when Bane arrived. Bane took the red sunglasses, the blue cap
    and the black jacket, but he did not steal the Golden Speaking Ball. In the library,
    the detective found an old diary by Fiona. Fiona was fascinated by the Golden
    Speaking Ball. She thought a teacher could enter rooms that students could not
    enter. She also thought that a teacher could blame somebody else. Now I know
    the truth.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0c5df167dbcd31e47b3956228346cfe1, type: 2}
