  m_text: 'Mrs Frogman:


    "Very well, Detective. Yes, I took the Golden Speaking
    Ball.

    I was fascinated by it for years. I wanted to discover what it could
    really do. Hidden doors, secret rooms, forgotten knowledge... Maybe even the
    power to change the world.

    Of course, the Ball is safe. I hid it in a secret
    compartment under the carpet. I had many brilliant ideas for it.

    You are
    clever ... do you want to help me and work together?"'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0c5df167dbcd31e47b3956228346cfe1, type: 2}
